Julia Stewart (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Julia_Stewart_(actress) 0 Julia Stewart (20 June 1862 – 12 December 1945) was an English actress. Beginning her career as a child actress, she went on to success on the London stage in adult roles in the late 1870s. She appeared on stage in New York from 1879.
